{"tid":2136353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三醫生組織倡公私合作增檢疫","createTime":"2020-08-02T05:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T05:48:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebba7cf3c4100c484bf7aaf02816d3caec21939","tid":2136353,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/S7H3GAUVG3RZNVN236FUQLPQ4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FS7H3GAUVG3RZNVN236FUQLPQ4A%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=9b4e1d3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FS7H3GAUVG3RZNVN236FUQLPQ4A%2F&h=2b9672fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/S7H3GAUVG3RZNVN236FUQLPQ4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n三醫生組織倡公私合作增檢疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jVepjDY9Cj6xVsSJqiDuFXvSZKU=/542x368/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3TGBKTBHA4SKCHZQ34XGU5SMM4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjVepjDY9Cj6xVsSJqiDuFXvSZKU%3D%2F542x368%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3TGBKTBHA4SKCHZQ34XGU5SMM4.gif&h=4ad6a272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳沛然<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎第三波7月爆發，連續11日確診個案均逾百宗，三個醫生組織發表聯合聲明，就公立醫院人手運用、病人處理、病毒檢測量等方面提出建議，亦促請政府減少不必要入境人士檢疫豁免。<br />\n<br />\n香港公共醫療醫生協會、香港醫學會、前線醫生聯盟聯同立法會議員陳沛然發表。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聲明建議，部份確診病人。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促減入境人士豁免<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：亞博啟用收30患者 走廊漏水<br />\n<br />\n對於檢測問題，組織指出，外界一直批評本港新冠病毒的每日檢測量嚴重不足，遠遠落後於新加坡和澳門，政府有必要提升衞生署的檢測能力，並透過加強公私營合作，提高每日檢測量，組織希望能增加檢測數目及縮短檢測報告時間。<br />\n<br />\n聲明引述多位專家指出，。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}